{
  "text": "2) MRF [CITATION_1] : Markov Random Fields based enhancement of LR depths with insight from the accompanied HR camera images under the assumption that depth discontinuities are usually in harmony with intensity changes in the associated camera image. contains HR textures and depths with lots of details [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "6748190",
